cusing on the prohibition era nixon's operation intercept and the post nafta years he received an undergraduate degree in art and art history from stanford university as well as a master's in history of art and architecture from harvard university he grew up in the borderland just outside el paso texas events & presentations the limits of sovereignty how the united states has policed its border with mexico since 1993 february 16 2012 cisac social science seminar cj alvarez edith sheffer search fsi search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages recent commentary cisac welcomes its 2011 2012 fellows september 3 2011 cisac fsi stanford announcement support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 4581 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
